    <Folder>
      <name>Intelligence Summary</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>AI Council Assessment</name>
        <styleUrl>#intel</styleUrl>
        <description>The current military posture indicates an increased presence in the Middle East, with the USS Boxer and its Amphibious Ready Group heading to the region. The US Air Force is conducting various missions, including transport, training, and patrol. The US Navy is also involved in maritime operations, with A-10 Warthogs patrolling the Strait of Hormuz. The situation in Iran is escalating, with reports of US forces striking suspected narco boats and Iranian energy infrastructure being targeted. The US Space Force is also active, with a recent exercise demonstrating its rapid launch capabilities. Overall, the military activity suggests a heightened state of alertness and readiness in response to emerging threats in the region.</description>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>0,0,0</coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
    </Folder>
